iser and the Graduate Committee of the department  Students are permitted and encouraged to follow interdisciplinary programs that may include more than one area of specialization and may require enrollment in courses in departments other than the Department of Chemical Engineering permanent adviser  Apply now GETTING STARTED Graduate Student Handbook   everything you need to know about Curriculum  Thesis preparation   Defense  Transfer procedures  Intent to Graduate Graduate Student Handbook Fellowships  Frequently Asked Questions  Frequently Asked Questions  Degree Requirements  Degree Requirements  Degree Requirements M S Course Approval Form M S Course Approval Form  Degree Requirements  Degree Requirements Ph D Course Approval Form Ph D Course Approval Form SPECIAL PROGRAMS     China Program  MS in Chemical Engineering     China Program  MS in Chemical Engineering Chemistry and Other Majors Can Apply for MS PhD in Chemical Engineering Chemistry and Other Majors Can Apply for MS PhD in Chemical Engineering GRADUATE FORMS D Students after they have chosen a permanent advisor Permanent Advisor Form  Meet with Faculty OTHER IMPORTANT LINKS General policies   procedures General policies   procedures  University Degree Requirements  University Degree Requirements Graduate Course Descriptions Graduate Course Descriptions UIC Schedule of Classes  UIC Schedule of Classes  Academic Calendar  Academic Calendar   r n    S Clinton St r nChicago  IL        r n    S Clinton St r nChicago  IL         cheuic uic edu               Future Students Undergraduate Studies Graduate Studies Seminars Scholarships Contact Us Laboratory Safety Forms Code of Ethics SaChE Program  nMake a Gift Make a Gift CookieSettings  University of Illinois Chicago  College of Engineering 